\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Frank did not spit out the words.
 He rather ushered them with profound force, hammering them at Martin Keller
 as if their roles had been suddenly reversed, and he was no longer the
 one on trial.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Quotes eld
